          "description": "Pediatric cardiology receptionist is the rudest person I\u2019ve come across. An appointment cancelled with no communication instead of apologising and taking the feedback to the doctor she\u2019s very confrontational on the phone instead of any customer service skills. Shocking. This appointment was for a 9 month old. Team needs to learn better manners with parents.",
