        {
          "username": "MommyMelly Mellsz",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "104035244289963325891",
          "user_review_count": 1,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPdU-y-TVaDJS47Hl6YnSGddfR1VXTGtPgKBPr5qePOLTKng=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "1st of I wanna say the staffs and doctors are very respectful the facility is extremely big and very clean and feels very welcoming I also wanna say I have quite a few kids and sometimes getting ready, even if I wake up extremely early and get us ready earlier ahead of time somehow I still get there late, which is on my end, but even if I get there extremely late, they would still see me what they would do it\u2019s just probably change your original time to the time that you came in once that doctor has availability. If not, then you will see a doctor that does that practice the same needs of your needs they have a beautiful fish tank and beautiful staff that play soft music with the kids while you wait. I will recommend this facility to anyone. They\u2019re all pretty cool showed laid-back but getting their job done on point with everything. Basically in and out, it\u2019s never a long waiting process with this office. God bless the doctors staff and nurse in this facility and everyone that visits this facility and everyone that\u2019s thinking of visiting this facility I say go for it. It won\u2019t hurt to give it a try if you don\u2019t like it you can always change, but I guarantee you will and you\u2019ll feel at home. God bless.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poSldXTkpkVlY2UkVWa1Z6UjRTMGxWY1UxVVZuYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x653199a7b6323431!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjhJWWNJdVV6REVkVzR4S0lVcU1UVnc%7C%7C?hl=en",
