          "description": "Avoid Dr Arpels-Josiah!  He is a fine Cardiologist, but Mt Sinai is unethical and has terrible customer support.  I had an annual test for many years and was charged the same amount each year.  When I told them it was my last test, they charged me an additional $10k \"Location Fee\" without any notice (not included in estimate).  They have been unresponsive and unhelpful when trying to resolve this. Be prepared for significant charges if you choose this location!",
